,"poster_path":"/voImabKBh1yzuOj7jfpApHuTW1s.jpg","release_date":"1979-11-30","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/5KpDP75GF9ThJGbH9nZImbI95Hj.jpg","original_title":"Io sto con gli ippopotami","original_language":"it"},{"id":41233,"adult":false,"title":"Step Up 3D","video":false,"overview":"A tight-knit group of New York City street dancers, including Luke and Natalie, team up with NYU freshman Moose, and find themselves pitted against the world's best hip-hop dancers in a high-stakes showdown that will change their lives forever.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4234,"vote_count":1970,"poster_path":"/rPcqa5TZ7S63RNmCuY45ZizFBen.jpg","release_date":"2010-08-04","vote_average":6.818,"backdrop_path":"/fboRjKzLF62ONXXen4e7D0msqTW.jpg","original_title":"Step Up 3D","original_language":"en"},{"id":52214,"adult":false,"title":"A Beautiful Wife","video":false,"overview":"Mariano has been married for 10 years with Miranda, a woman way out of his league. Their small-town life is disrupted by womanizing photographer Andrea, who — struck by her good looks — offers Miranda a one-time modelling job. Albeit hesitant, the couple eventually accepts his invitation to the Seychelles...","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4425,"vote_count":483,"poster_path":"/4nXWGRq30f9gQfRuiQoXZjvClvJ.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-14","vote_average":5.731,"backdrop_path":"/bro3aAx14EfSG5SQqL4P3mLDkfe.jpg","original_title":"Una moglie bellissima","original_language":"it"},{"id":43200,"adult":false,"title":"Basilicata Coast to Coast","video":false,"overview":"A music group and a journalist cross the region of Basilicata by foot to attend a music festival.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4606,"vote_count":393,"poster_path":"/1jFrV9DPPS38jgYgyUFJXukMsAt.jpg","release_date":"2010-04-09","vote_average":6.295,"backdrop_path":"/38W3ELhUprf0aTWyviRggCs1Jmi.jpg","original_title":"Basilicata Coast to Coast","original_language":"it"},{"id":12230,"adult":false,"title":"One Hundred and One Dalmatians","video":false,"overview":"When a litter of dalmatian puppies are abducted by the minions of Cruella De Vil, the parents must find them before she uses them for a diabolical fashion statement.","genre_ids":[12,16,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.1825,"vote_count":6587,"poster_path":"/kSlYq6FrBUviGSEh8v4L9nrSnBT.jpg","release_date":"1961-01-25","vote_average":7.173,"backdrop_path":"/cZgUATpU4NDlsfGj7sRriKJEiLB.jpg","original_title":"One Hundred and One Dalmatians","original_language":"en"},{"id":7091,"adult":false,"title":"Vampire's Kiss","video":false,"overview":"A publishing executive is visited and bitten by a vampire and starts exhibiting erratic behavior. He pushes his secretary to extremes as he tries to come to terms with his affliction.","genre_ids":[35,27,80,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4756,"vote_count":472,"poster_path":"/bEwvlXvvrVLPFwCOND5E38qly01.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-02","vote_average":5.918,"backdrop_path":"/rrmavNBz1aKSY11jbGGnj1Q5CTo.jpg","original_title":"Vampire's Kiss","original_language":"en"},{"id":282963,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Who: Planet of the Dead","video":false,"overview":"A meeting in a London bus with jewel thief Lady Christina takes a turn for the worse for the Doctor when the bus takes a detour to a desert-like planet, where the deadly Swarm awaits.","genre_ids":[878,10770,53,14,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6264,"vote_count":218,"poster_path":"/9qKoF7XjkcbWYwekBCKt7W7rDHc.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-11","vote_average":7.495,"backdrop_path":"/umWItKKGIVcI9iq2IlIrQp0s9F4.jpg","original_title":"Doctor Who: Planet of the Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":16665,"adult":false,"title":"Whisky Galore!","video":false,"overview":"Based on a true story. The name of the real ship, that sunk Feb 5 1941 - during WWII - was S/S Politician. Having left Liverpool two days earlier, heading for Jamaica, it sank outside Eriskay, The Outer Hebrides, Scotland, in bad weather, containing 250,000 bottles of whisky. The locals gathered as many bottles as they could, before the proper authorities arrived, and even today, bottles are found in the sand or in the sea every other year.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4911,"vote_count":147,"poster_path":"/4qz5Oc3hgXx4eBx7vkqLfG58J9X.jpg","release_date":"1949-06-16","vote_average":6.81,"backdrop_path":"/y1siOoSCQ4oLBo05F3STFia7tVb.jpg","original_title":"Whisky Galore!","original_language":"en"},{"id":33666,"adult":false,"title":"The Glass Bottom Boat","video":false,"overview":"Bruce, the owner of an aerospace company, is infatuated with Jennifer and hires her to be his biographer so that he can be near her and win her affections. Is she actually a Russian spy trying to obtain aerospace secrets?","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5783,"vote_count":65,"poster_path":"/jlj5rCl7jfW7QskJ1vucd7j5n5M.jpg","release_date":"1966-06-09","vote_average":6.246,"backdrop_path":"/cQ9sbPLBox8z2LIYsExHnsvgrzZ.jpg","original_title":"The Glass Bottom Boat","original_language":"en"},{"id":5689,"adult":false,"title":"The Blue Lagoon","video":false,"overview":"Two small children and a ship's cook survive a shipwreck and find safety on an idyllic tropical island. Soon, however, the cook dies and the young boy and girl are left on their own. Days become years and Emmeline and Richard make a home for themselves surrounded by exotic creatures and nature's beauty. But will they ever see civilization again?","genre_ids":[12,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.7233,"vote_count":1975,"poster_path":"/k6KsThCeoxxHDbVnlHLdTlf5wsy.jpg","release_date":"1980-07-05","vote_average":6.145,"backdrop_path":"/4HYBkZPz2Gb7LWXludvvOfATzGS.jpg","original_title":"The Blue Lagoon","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":null,"twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":108288,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"zh","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-03-21T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"original_network":null,"screenwriters":null,"based_on":null,"filming_location":null,"narrative_location":null,"review_score_rt":null,"review_score_mc":null,"box_office":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"collection_id":null,"wikidata_metadata":{},"mood_tags":null,"trope_tags":null,"vibe_description":null,"ai_enriched_at":null,"ai_enrichment_version":0}}]]
9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"King of Painting | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Ke Huan is a talented and dreamy painter, but in this \"era of hype by all\", he became a joke in Tangzhuang, a painter village, because he was busy painting. Just when he couldn't pay the rent, was bullied by his peers, and his girlfriend was stolen by his rival, an alien changed his fate! With the help of \"it\"'s superpowers, the protagonist Ke Huan drove a luxury car, lived in a luxury house, held his dream exhibition, became a hot painter, and reached the peak of his life! The arrival of \"it\" also caused trouble everywhere, shocked the world, and caused panic among the people. The police, opponents, and even aliens came to the door one after another."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108288/king-of-painting"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"King of Painting"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Ke Huan is a talented and dreamy painter, but in this \"era of hype by all\", he became a joke in Tangzhuang, a painter village, because he was busy painting. Just when he couldn't pay the rent, was bullied by his peers, and his girlfriend was stolen by his rival, an alien changed his fate! With the help of \"it\"'s superpowers, the protagonist Ke Huan drove a luxury car, lived in a luxury house, held his dream exhibition, became a hot painter, and reached the peak of his life! The arrival of \"it\" also caused trouble everywhere, shocked the world, and caused panic among the people. The police, opponents, and even aliens came to the door one after another."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108288/king-of-painting"}],["